            {
               "text": "<p><center><div class=\"first_steps_lab_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_lab question_mark\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-microscope\"></i></div><div class=\"first_steps_lab\"><b>Practice 1</b><br />If you have <b>Table 1</b> with you, color the numbers in it.<br /> Alternatively, copy them onto a piece of paper and color them as you wish.</p>",
