         "id": "SECTION_conclusion",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>Conclusion</h3>We have learned about the Hindu-Arabic numbers and their relationship with our fingers. There are many other numerical systems and many things we can do with them, but before we proceed, in the next page we will reinforce our knowledge with some fun activities.</p>",
